    {
      "id": "39",
      "name": "推薦角色和相關資訊",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "推薦角色",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 23,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Venti_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "溫迪",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "絕弦是最適合溫迪的一把四星武器！溫迪的元素戰技與元素爆發可以對敵人造成可觀的傷害，即便是作為輔助，也可以提高戰鬥能力，絕弦的被動效果也放大了溫迪的這個優點。同時，絕弦的副屬性所提供的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素精通",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "，也很適合風元素的角色。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 42,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Tartaglia_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "達達利亞",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "除了提高元素戰技與元素爆發的傷害，該武器的元素精通還對達達利亞觸發蒸發反應的元素爆發傷害有很大的提高，比較適合達達利亞使用。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2268,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/08/24/7998136/37a18b6b6865c59063003a9380f08225_1266672008615328646.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "柯萊",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器對",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素精通",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "的提高以及對元素戰技和元素爆發的傷害增加，都能夠有效提升柯萊打出的激化反應傷害。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 38,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Fischl_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "菲謝爾",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "絕弦適合於定位於輔助輸出位置的菲謝爾。首先，絕弦的被動效果可以增加奧茲的輸出傷害，其次，絕弦的副屬性所提供的元素精通也提高了奧茲所造成的反應傷害，特別是以達達利亞為主要輸出角色的元素隊伍中，使用絕弦作為武器的菲謝爾有著不錯的表現。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "獲得方法",
